data.description: Introducing this swanky mid-century modern beauty located right in the heart of the highly sought-after Poth school district.  This home boasts 3 spacious bedrooms and not one, but two large bathrooms that'll make you feel like you're in a spa retreat. huge washroom - perfect for all your laundering needs. Plantation shutters though out. This home has been cared for with love and updated over the years. Side porch, just perfect for sipping on your Hot chocolate as you watch the world go by, And if you're looking for a bit more privacy, we've got you covered with a more secluded porch out back.  The primary bedroom is big enough for a king-size bed, so you can sleep like a king or queen. You'll also find a designated dining area right off the kitchen. Beautiful floors throughout the home, and we can't forget those charming 1950's built-ins scattered throughout the home. This four-sides brick dream is ready for its next chapter, and it could be you!
